cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.DC

This paper deals with the security of power grids against cyber-attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also uses analytical models and grid context information to estimate the security situation, which involves system control and optimization (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Intrusion Detection Systems and firewalls also falls under the category of network and internet architecture (cs.NI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
